name: Tangen
toy_description: Tengen Uzui, also known as the Sound Hashira, is a character from the manga and anime series Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba. He is one of the nine Hashira, the elite swordsmen of the Demon Slayer Corps.

name: Sanemi
toy_description: Sanemi Shinazugawa, also known as the Wind Hashira, is a character from the manga and anime series Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba. He is one of the nine Hashira, the elite swordsmen of the Demon Slayer Corps.

name: Giyu
toy_description: Giyu Tomioka, also known as the Water Hashira, is a prominent character in the manga and anime series Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba. He is one of the nine Hashira, the elite swordsmen of the Demon Slayer Corps.

name: Shinobu
toy_description: A Shinobu Doll refers to a merchandise item inspired by the character Shinobu Kocho from the anime and manga series Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba.

name: Tanjiro
toy_description: The Tanjiro doll is a popular collectible item among fans of the anime series Demon Slayer. The Tanjiro doll serves as a reminder of the incredible journey and inspiring qualities of this beloved anime character.

name: Zinetsu
toy_description: Zenitsu Doll refers to a merchandise item inspired by the character Zenitsu Agatsuma from the anime and manga series Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba. Zenitsu is a complex character known for his cowardice, lightning-based swordsmanship, and his distinctive yellow pigtail.

name: Inosuke
toy_description: An Inosuke Doll refers to a merchandise item inspired by the character Inosuke Hashibira from the anime and manga series Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba. Inosuke is a fierce and wild member of the Demon Slayer Corps.

name: Kokoshibo
toy_description: Kokoshibo is a character from the popular manga and anime series Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba. Kokoshibo, also known as Kokushibo or the Upper Moon One, is one of the Twelve Kizuki, the strongest demons serving under the main antagonist, Muzan Kibutsuji.

name: Mujan
toy_description: The main antagonist of the series is Muzan Kibutsuji, who is the leader of the demons and the primary target of the Demon Slayer Corps.

name: Doma
toy_description: Doma is a character from the manga and anime series Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba. He is one of the Twelve Kizuki, the upper-ranking members of the demons serving under Muzan Kibutsuji.
